# Closing Checklist

Read when: before final handoff, when the operator says "run the closing checklist", "run closeout", "prove the checklist", or asks whether everything required is done.
Skip when: the task is still actively blocked and the final answer is only a status update.

Purpose: final session closeout gate. The AI must report PASS / FAIL / N/A for each item before saying the work is done.

## Closing Gate

| Check | Result | Evidence / Note |
|---|---|---|
| User request answered | PASS / FAIL | |
| Scope stayed within request | PASS / FAIL | |
| Acceptance criteria checked | PASS / FAIL / N/A | |
| Workflow mode checked | PASS / N/A | `docs/SCENARIO_PLAYBOOK.md` decision recorded or cloud-only/local-mode N/A |
| Plan updated | PASS / N/A | `docs/GAME_PLAN.md` or `docs/PROJECT_CANVAS.md` |
| Session brief synced | PASS / N/A | `bash scripts/sync_session_brief.sh` |
| Tests / commands run | PASS / FAIL / N/A | list commands and exit results |
| Verify gate run | PASS / FAIL / N/A | Project verify command or reason skipped |
| Worker DONE packet reviewed | PASS / N/A | `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md` |
| Traceability updated | PASS / N/A | Path IDs / smoke evidence |
| Docs / changelog updated | PASS / N/A | files updated or reason skipped |
| UI-visible evidence checked | PASS / N/A | browser smoke, screenshot/trace, or manual click path |
| Data safety checked | PASS / N/A | snapshot/restore evidence or no data touched |
| Security/privacy risk checked | PASS / N/A | scan/review note |
| Open risks listed | PASS / FAIL | risks or `None` |
| Remaining work listed | PASS / FAIL | follow-ups or `None` |

## Required Final Handoff Shape

After running the checklist, answer with:

- What changed
- Commands/tests run and results
- Closing checklist summary
- Open risks or follow-ups
- Whether the work is done, blocked, or waiting on operator action

Do not claim DONE if any required item is FAIL. Say what is blocked and what exact next action would clear it.